# 15.3 Phase 1 — Persistent Report Storage

Current

```
Docker

↓

/app/reports
```

Problem

Docker containers are ephemeral.

Reports disappear when the container restarts.

Future Architecture

```
Filesystem MCP

↓

Amazon S3

or

Google Cloud Storage

or

Azure Blob Storage

↓

Permanent Storage
```

Benefits

- Persistent reports
- Download links
- Report history
- Sharing capability

