# 15.20 Final Vision

The Study Abroad Finder demonstrates far more than an AI-powered university recommendation system.

It establishes a reusable architectural blueprint for building modular, tool-augmented AI applications using Google ADK and the Model Context Protocol.

As additional capabilities are introduced—persistent storage, authentication, multi-agent collaboration, vector search, observability, governance, and enterprise integrations—the same core architecture can evolve into a scalable AI platform capable of supporting a wide variety of business domains.

The project therefore represents both a functional application and a reference architecture for future AI systems built around standardized tool orchestration and intelligent reasoning.